t: "Tiyimmatin ad ssuĂźvent arraw nnsent, sin iseggwasen mden, i win ib$an ad itim ussuĂźev. ÂŁef ubabat, lmakla akked lebsa nnsent, s lqanun. Ur ipwakellaf yiman siwa ar wayen iwumi izmer. Tarwa ur teĂźĂźuĂŽĂŽu imma s, ur teĂźĂźuĂŽĂŽu baba s. I uweĂŽĂŽat, am akka. Ma b$an ad kksen tuĂźĂźva, mcawaĂŽen, ulac u$ilif fellasen. Ma teb$am tamĂŽebbit, a ppessuĂźĂźev tarwa nnwen, ulac u$ilif fellawen, ma txelĂ»em ayen i wen ilaqen, s lqanun. Ăezzbet i Ăebbi. Cfut ar Ăebbi Ipwali ayen txeddmem"